title-of-article: Here is the full list of winners from the 2019 Frame Awards
content:
Amsterdam – In the second edition of the Frame Awards, which took place last night at De Kromhouthal in Amsterdam, we truly celebrated the outstanding and sometimes illuminatingly unexpected qualities that make up the future of spatial design. Both our jury members and the Frame readers selected the best projects of the year in categories from hospitality to set design, from retail to residential.

Here is the full list of this year's winners.
